    "Twenty-one studies were peer-reviewed journal articles.",
    "Study locations included Australia (1), Canada (1), Chile (1), Chile, Colombia, and Mexico (1), Italy (1), most European countries (1), Pakistan (3), Sweden (1), the USA (46), and the UK (2).",
